# CMS

CMS is simple blog content management system API allowing creation and modification of articles and their comments.

# Group Articles

Resources related to articles in the API.

## Articles Collection [/articles]

### List All Articles [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "author": "Pepa",
                "title": "Muj prvni clanek",
                "creation_date": "2018-01-27T08:55:15",
                "updated_date": "2018-01-27T09:55:15",
                "url": "/articles/1"
            }
        ]

### Create a New Article [POST]

You may create your own article using this action. It takes JSON object containing author, title and the actual content.

+ author (string) - Author of the article
+ title (string) - Article title
+ content (string) - Article content

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "author": "Pepa",
            "title": "Muj prvni clanek",
            "content": "Hello world, toto je muj prvni clanek"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /articles/1

    + Body

            {
                "author": "Pepa",
                "title": "Muj prvni clanek",
                "creation_date": "2018-01-27T08:55:15",
                "url": "/articles/1"
                "content": "Hello world, toto je muj prvni clanek"
            }

## Article [/articles/{article_id}]

+ Parameters
    + article_id (number) - ID of the Article in the form of an integer

