### Article Comments Collection [/articles/{article_id}/comments]

#### List All Article Comments [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "author": "Martin",
                "creation_date": "2018-01-27T09:30:15",
                "url": "/articles/1/comments/1"
                "content": "S obsahem tohoto clanku nesouhlasim"
            }
        ]

#### Create a New Article Comment [POST]

You may comment an article using this action. It takes JSON object containing author and the actual comment content.

+ author (string) - Author of the comment
+ content (string) - Comment body

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "author": "Martin",
            "content": "S obsahem tohoto clanku nesouhlasim"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /articles/1/comments/1

    + Body

            {
                "author": "Martin",
                "creation_date": "2018-01-27T09:30:15",
                "url": "/articles/1/comments/1"
                "content": "S obsahem tohoto clanku nesouhlasim"
            }

### Article Comment [/articles/{article_id}/comments/{comment_id}]

+ Parameters
    + comment_id (number) - ID of the Article Comment in the form of an integer. Unique for given article.

#### Delete [DELETE]

+ Response 204
